gw.api.web.producer.agencybill

Class AgencyBillMoneyReceivedSetup<T extends BaseMoneyReceived,D extends AgencyCycleDist>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.web.producer.agencybill.AgencyBillMoneyReceivedSetup<T,D>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AgencyBillPaymentMoneySetup, AgencyBillPromisedMoneySetup

    public abstract class AgencyBillMoneyReceivedSetup<T extends BaseMoneyReceived,D extends AgencyCycleDist>
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class to help with the creation of Agency Bill Distributions and Monies. This class helps with the setup of the details of the Agency Bill Money (whether it be a promise money or a payment money) and what InvoiceItems the distribution that eventually is created to distribute the money should target. It also sets up the connection between the money wrapped by this setup, and the appropriate distribution For instantiating AgencyBillMoneyReceivedSetups, see AgencyBillMoneySetupFactory
